track.name: Devil In A New Dress
comments: The crib Scarface, could it be more Tony? You love me for me, could you be more phony?
Rick Ross held it down on here.
The height of Rick Ross' career. [2] HUH
The height of Rick Ross' career.
There is only one true Rick Ross..."Freeway" Rick Ross. I would have preferred the second half of the song only be instrumental...
hard work pays off.. kanye is proof of that, no matter how arrogant he is. great stuff.

The most underrated song on MBDTF.  Kanye's best lines (I ordered the jerk, she said you are what you eat), Rick Ross' best storytelling, the beautiful guitar interlude, and that one massive guitar lick.
looking at my wrist will turn ur ass 2 stone, looking at my bitch will give ur ass a bone
